    <h2 class="section-title">GTD electric, GFD Profile front-load, Café, and gas variants.</h2>

    <p class="lead">A representative sample of GE dryer model families our techs service routinely. Not exhaustive, GE's catalog is broad, but covers the units that show up most often on our route.</p>

    <div class="model-grid">
      <div class="model-card">
